<i>MARGE:
Glory turned to fiasco</i>

113
00:05:05,277 --> 00:05:08,017
<i>for the disgraced
Mayor of Springfield,</i>

114
00:05:08,116 --> 00:05:10,116
<i>Eustace Van Houten.</i>

115
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,960
(coughs)

116
00:05:11,957 --> 00:05:14,427
Aw, soup crackers.

117
00:05:14,529 --> 00:05:16,929
- MAN 1: Charlatan!
- MAN 2: Mountebank!

118
00:05:17,034 --> 00:05:18,574
WOMAN:
Dunderhead!

119
00:05:18,571 --> 00:05:21,581
Dad, was he
one of our relatives?

120
00:05:21,577 --> 00:05:25,277
Yeah, he was your
great-great-grandfather.

121
00:05:25,417 --> 00:05:27,557
Not so great, I guess.

122
00:05:27,555 --> 00:05:31,055
So, the Van Houtens
have always been losers.

123
00:05:31,162 --> 00:05:33,772
Not true, son.
Hey, your granddad

124
