right at the table.
(chuckles)

126
00:05:38,443 --> 00:05:41,553
Fine, Dad.
I'm gonna go to Phys Ed.

127
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:44,390
We're doing swimming today.

128
00:05:50,066 --> 00:05:51,196
Mm...

129
