144
00:06:26,673 --> 00:06:28,883
Shaq, you suckered me again.

145
00:06:28,877 --> 00:06:31,977
Hey, hey, hey.
I will not have you badmouthing

146
00:06:31,984 --> 00:06:33,424
Shaquille Rashaun O'Neal.

147
00:06:33,419 --> 00:06:34,989
Four-time NBA champ,

148
00:06:35,090 --> 00:06:36,790
rapper, actor, sheriff,

149
00:06:36,793 --> 00:06:39,433
restaurateur,
black belt in Shaq-Fu,

150
00:06:39,431 --> 00:06:41,201
Shaq belt in kung fu,

151
00:06:41,202 --> 00:06:43,042
and now
the Big Aristotle dominates

152
00:06:43,039 --> 00:06:44,209
the late-night airwaves.

153
00:06:44,208 --> 00:06:46,348
