- What the hell were we thinking?
- (Marge grumbles)

192
00:08:22,104 --> 00:08:23,414
I know Kirk is angry,

193
00:08:23,406 --> 00:08:25,206
but I'm a little worried
this meeting

194
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:27,050
will go off the rails.

195
