Stop teaching facts!

238
00:10:04,542 --> 00:10:06,582
Historical guilt is everything.

239
00:10:06,713 --> 00:10:09,753
You snowflakes
are hurting our feelings.

240
00:10:09,853 --> 00:10:12,263
Those who cannot
remember the past

241
00:10:12,257 --> 00:10:13,987
are condemned to repeat it.

242
00:10:14,094 --> 00:10:17,274
On the other hand, those
who cannot remember the past

243
00:10:17,267 --> 00:10:19,507
are condemned to repeat it.

244
00:10:19,606 --> 00:10:21,906
People, people, people!
People.

245
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:24,650
We are not
going to settle this tonight.

246
00:10:24,649 --> 00:10:26,619
I move that we end this meeting

247
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,720
with everyone
angry and dissatisfied.

248
00:10:28,724 --> 00:10:30,134
All in favor?

249
00:10:30,126 --> 00:10:31,626
ALL:
Boo!

250
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:33,800
Wonderful.
It's unanimous.

251
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:34,640
Mm.

252
00:10:34,736 --> 00:10:36,636
Dad, I know this
is a weird thing

253
00:10:36,640 --> 00:10:38,780
for a son to say to his father,

254
00:10:38,877 --> 00:10:40,707
but I'm proud of you.

255
00:10:40,815 --> 00:10:43,345
You actually convinced people.

256
00:10:43,452 --> 00:10:44,622
I did?

257
00:10:44,756 --> 00:10:46,456
You the man, Kirk.

258
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:49,600
- I am?
